<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国 - 南华早报</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/rss/4/feed</link><description>来自中国的最新突发新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 23:22:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>学者警告称，中国经济增长面临社会停滞的风险，这是“我们这个时代最严重的危机”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3252459/chinas-economic-growth-risk-societal-stagnation-scholar-warns-most-significant-crisis-our-time?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>武汉大学专门研究农村治理的社会学教授卢德文警告说，在中国经济复苏乏力的情况下，存在一种肤浅而非实质的趋势。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 22:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3252459/chinas-economic-growth-risk-societal-stagnation-scholar-warns-most-significant-crisis-our-time?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，一些滞留的俄罗斯索科尔石油货物开始运往中国和印度</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3252492/some-stranded-russian-sokol-oil-cargoes-begin-move-china-and-india-data-shows?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>据数据分析公司 Kpler 称，其中两艘油轮 NS Century 和 Nellis 正在向中国港口运送总计 220 万桶索科尔油。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 17:45:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3252492/some-stranded-russian-sokol-oil-cargoes-begin-move-china-and-india-data-shows?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>在致命的船只事故后，中国海警登上了台湾游轮</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3252490/chinese-coastguard-boarded-taiwan-cruise-ship-after-deadly-boat-incident?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>北京方面表示，在上周造成两名中国公民死亡的船只事故后，将加强巡逻。台北海岸警卫队表示，在周一的事件中，有 6 名大陆官员登上了这艘船。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 17:02:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3252490/chinese-coastguard-boarded-taiwan-cruise-ship-after-deadly-boat-incident?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>为什么时隔三十多年，中国外长仍以非洲之行作为新年伊始</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252446/why-after-more-3-decades-chinas-foreign-minister-still-starts-year-trip-africa?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>自从钱其琛1991年开始召开大会以来，出访的时间一直保持一致，但其目的发生了变化。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 14:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252446/why-after-more-3-decades-chinas-foreign-minister-still-starts-year-trip-africa?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>台湾将与法国国防部签订价值 7,900 万美元的零件采购协议，升级拉斐特级护卫舰</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3252471/taiwan-upgrade-lafayette-class-frigates-under-us79-million-deal-parts-french-defence-ministry-arm?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>国防部消息人士告诉《华盛顿邮报》，早该进行的升级是台湾海军面对北京日益增长的军事压力而进行现代化努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 13:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3252471/taiwan-upgrade-lafayette-class-frigates-under-us79-million-deal-parts-french-defence-ministry-arm?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着市场竞争加剧，中国电动汽车制造商华人运通暂停豪华高合品牌的生产六个月</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/business/china-business/article/3252473/chinese-ev-maker-human-horizons-suspends-manufacture-luxury-hiphi-brand-6-months-market-competition?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>据当地财经媒体界面报道，总部位于上海的华人运通周日告诉其员工，将暂停其豪华高合品牌六个月，立即生效。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 12:38:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/business/china-business/article/3252473/chinese-ev-maker-human-horizons-suspends-manufacture-luxury-hiphi-brand-6-months-market-competition?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着中国电子商务巨头将目光投向海外，京东考虑收购英国电子零售商 Currys</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3252464/jdcom-considers-takeover-bid-uk-electronics-retailer-currys-chinas-e-commerce-giants-look-overseas?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>京东可能竞购英国咖喱，正值中国大型电子商务企业在国内竞争加剧和经济逆风的情况下继续寻求海外增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 12:30:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3252464/jdcom-considers-takeover-bid-uk-electronics-retailer-currys-chinas-e-commerce-giants-look-overseas?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国科学家研制出等离子体隐形装置，使军用飞机脱离雷达</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3251401/chinese-scientists-create-plasma-stealth-device-take-military-aircraft-radar?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>研究人员开发了一种新型等离子隐形装置，可能会改变军用飞机的游戏规则。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 12:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3251401/chinese-scientists-create-plasma-stealth-device-take-military-aircraft-radar?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促美国停止“无故”在边境“骚扰”中国学生</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252452/china-urges-us-stop-harassing-its-students-border-no-reason?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国公安部部长王晓红在维也纳对美国国防部长亚历杭德罗·马约卡斯表示，美国必须确保中国公民“公平入境待遇和充分尊严”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 11:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252452/china-urges-us-stop-harassing-its-students-border-no-reason?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国国产C919客机在新加坡展翅高飞 首次国际亮相</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3252436/chinas-home-grown-c919-passenger-jet-takes-wing-singapore-international-debut?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>备受关注的国产客机C919首次亮相国际舞台，成为新加坡航展的一大亮点。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:00:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3252436/chinas-home-grown-c919-passenger-jet-takes-wing-singapore-international-debut?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>魅族、OPPO 等中国智能手机厂商在 2024 年行业复苏的背景下加大了人工智能在其设备中的集成力度</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-trends/article/3252439/chinese-smartphone-vendors-meizu-oppo-step-ai-integration-their-devices-amid-expected-industry?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国手机中人工智能集成的增加表明，随着全球市场有望在 2024 年复苏，智能手机行业的新技术军备竞赛正在升温。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 09:30:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-trends/article/3252439/chinese-smartphone-vendors-meizu-oppo-step-ai-integration-their-devices-amid-expected-industry?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国未来的强国湖南希望官员“解放思想”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3252412/chinas-would-be-powerhouse-hunan-wants-officials-emancipate-their-minds?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>“平躺”政策已经结束，有效振兴全省经济的努力已经开始，这场运动针对的是各级共产党干部。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 09:00:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3252412/chinas-would-be-powerhouse-hunan-wants-officials-emancipate-their-minds?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>王毅表示，中国和西班牙同意提供“公平、非歧视”的营商环境</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252411/china-germany-should-stick-openness-and-free-trade-and-keep-policy-predictable-wang-yi-says?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>北京将取消长达24年的西班牙牛肉进口禁令，中国外交部长称这是“好消息，特别是对西班牙农民来说”。王毅在与西班牙外长阿尔瓦雷斯会谈后表示，双方同意扩大新领域合作。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 07:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252411/china-germany-should-stick-openness-and-free-trade-and-keep-policy-predictable-wang-yi-says?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>国家能源局局长表示，中国的气候目标：能源消耗不断增长、脱碳进展缓慢带来挑战</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/business/china-business/article/3252406/chinas-climate-goals-growing-energy-consumption-slow-progress-decarbonisation-pose-challenges-says?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>国家能源局（NEA）负责人表示，中国不断增长的能源消耗、脱碳进程的缓慢以及新能源装机容量的限制，对这个世界上最大的温室气体排放国的气候目标构成了重大挑战。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 06:08:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/business/china-business/article/3252406/chinas-climate-goals-growing-energy-consumption-slow-progress-decarbonisation-pose-challenges-says?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>全球影响：中国对以色列-加沙战争和红海危机的反应反映了其世界强国的哪些地位？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3252365/global-impact-what-does-chinas-response-israel-gaza-war-and-red-sea-crisis-say-about-its-position?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在本期《全球影响》时事通讯中，我们关注北京对以色列-加沙战争和胡塞叛军袭击扰乱全球航运后的红海危机的反应。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 06:00:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3252365/global-impact-what-does-chinas-response-israel-gaza-war-and-red-sea-crisis-say-about-its-position?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item></channel></rss>